com.hawkore.mule.extensions.sap.internal.errors

Class ModuleExceptionMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hawkore.mule.extensions.sap.internal.errors.ModuleExceptionMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConnectorExceptionVisitor<org.mule.runtime.extension.api.exception.ModuleException>

    public class ModuleExceptionMapper
extends Object
implements IConnectorExceptionVisitor<org.mule.runtime.extension.api.exception.ModuleException>
    Maps a exception to a ModuleException. This class is designed to be used at every operation to map any exception to a mule ModuleException.

    See also map(Throwable).

    Author:
    Manuel Núñez Sánchez (manuel.nunez@hawkore.com)
